
				                 ANC delegates have clearly decided where Zuma should migrate to as he prepares to step down as ANC president.
The governing party’s delegates suggested through song that he should leave for Dubai:




If you think Zuma was the only one who was rebelled against at the ANC’s 54th national conference, presidential candidate Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma was also on the receiving end of the bad rep. Delegates sang in Zulu that “this road is hard, it has Zuma and his wife”.
